goals.question: What is the seasonal pattern of CO2 concentration?

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['Date'])]
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.plot(data['Date'], data['CO2'], color='blue', label='CO2')
    ax.plot(data['Date'], data['adjusted_CO2'], color='red', label='Adjusted CO2')
    ax.set_xlabel('Year')
    ax.set_ylabel('CO2 Concentration')
    ax.set_title('What is the trend of CO2 concentration over time?')
    ax.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['CO2'], bins=30, color='green')
    plt.axvline(data['CO2'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean: {data['CO2'].mean():.2f}")
    plt.axvline(data['CO2'].median(), color='blue', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {data['CO2'].median():.2f}")
    plt.xlabel('CO2 Concentration')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of CO2 concentration?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 6))
    ax.boxplot([data['CO2'], data['adjusted_CO2']])
    ax.set_xticklabels(['CO2', 'Adjusted CO2'])
    ax.set_ylabel('Concentration')
    plt.title('What is the difference between CO2 and adjusted CO2 concentration?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['Date'])]
    data['Month'] = data['Date'].dt.month
    monthly_co2 = data.groupby('Month')['CO2'].mean()
    plt.plot(monthly_co2.index, monthly_co2.values, color='blue')
    plt.xlabel('Month')
    plt.ylabel('CO2 Concentration')
    plt.title('What is the seasonal pattern of CO2 concentration?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```
